data.description: ****Selling Short Sale*** Nothing to do but move into this beautiful 3 bedroom ranch with an attached garage. The generously sized kitchen includes all stainless steel appliances and the open concept from kitchen to the dining area unto the living room is great for day to day living and entertaining. The sliding doors off of the dining room lead to the patio and fully fenced in yard.  The furnace and A/C are less than 6 years old. **Sold As/Is **Seller related to LA.
